snippet.title: Don Duality - Official Gameplay Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for Don Duality to see gameplay and various features of this upcoming tycoon game with card mechanics. In Don Duality, send your gangsters to beat out debts, rob banks, steal valuables and launder the money they earn in your establishment. Hire staff for your restaurant and upgrade it, but be careful. Not many people can sit on two chairs at once. Don Duality will be available on PC.

#GameTrailers #SoG
